"        U.S. Preventive Services Task Force: Screening for Breast Cancer. U.S. Preventive Services Task Force 2009.",
"       </li>",
"       <li>",
"        Rahimtoola SH. Choice of prosthetic heart valve in adults an update. J Am Coll Cardiol 2010; 55:2413.",
"       </li>",
"       <li>",
"        Walter LC, Lindquist K, Nugent S, et al. Impact of age and comorbidity on colorectal cancer screening among older veterans. Ann Intern Med 2009; 150:465.",
"       </li>",
